  <description><![CDATA[<p>Offering an central location in Niederau, the Hotel Harfenwirt is a traditional hotel with great views across the valley.</p>
<h2>Location</h2>
<p>The hotel has a great location opposite the Tennladen lift and nursery slopes. The ski bus stops outside making it very easy to explore the whole <a rel="noopener" data-udi="umb://document/cd224c7e0dd048d9bf01141d900a327a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cd224c7e0dd048d9bf01141d900a327a}" target="_blank" title="The Ski Juwel Area">Ski Juwel</a> area.</p>
<p>It's only a few minutes stroll along the road into the village centre for access to the main Markbachjoch gondola, après ski or a bit of nightlife.</p>]]></description>
