  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Standard Austrian twin</strong> rooms are 20-25<span>m² and can sleep up to three using a double sofa bed. They are in the original building and have a bath with showerhead and a balcony.</span></p>
<p><strong>Superior</strong> <strong>Austrian twin</strong> rooms are around 30<span>m² and can also sleep up to three. These rooms are in the newer wing and have a bath, seating area and a balcony.</span></p>
<p><strong>Single </strong>rooms are around 20<span>m². They </span>are in the original wing and have a shower.</p>
<p><strong>Bedroom Facilities</strong></p>
